com.preemptive.annotation.instrumentation

Annotation Type Application


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value={TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,METHOD})
public @interface Application
    Defines information about the application.

    This annotation can specify these values for the application:

    • ID - GUID format
    • type - free form text
    • name - free form text
    • version - free form text

    These values are used by ApplicationStart. Values specified at the class level are inherited at the method where ApplicationStart is used.

    See Also:
    ApplicationStart, ApplicationId, ApplicationName, ApplicationType, ApplicationVersion, ApplicationVersionSource, Dynamic Properties
